{"title_page": "S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng District", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng District\n|settlement_type        = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = Huy\u1ec7n S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng\n|nickname               = \n|motto                  = \n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = \n|pushpin_label_position = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Vietnam}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces of Vietnam|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[B\u1eafc Giang Province|B\u1eafc Giang]]\n|subdivision_type2      = \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|seat_type              = Capital\n|seat                   = [[An Ch\u00e2u, B\u1eafc Giang|An Ch\u00e2u]]\n|government_type        =\n|leader_title           = \n|leader_name            = \n| leader_title1          = Party Secretary:\n| leader_name1           = Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0\u1edfng<ref>http://www.bacgiang.gov.vn/email/c-210/timkiem.html&c=0</ref>\n| leader_title2          = People's Council Chairman:\n| leader_name2           = Nguy\u1ec5n Quang Ng\u1ea1n\n| leader_title3          = People's Committee Chairman:  <!-- for places with, say, both a mayor and a city manager -->\n| leader_name3           = Ho\u00e0ng My Ca\n|established_title      =  \n|established_date       = \n|area_magnitude         = \n|unit_pref              = Imperial<!--Enter: Imperial, if Imperial (metric) is desired-->\n|area_footnotes         = \n|area_total_km2         = 844 \n|area_land_km2          = \n|area_water_km2         = \n|area_total_sq_mi       = \n|area_land_sq_mi        = \n|area_water_sq_mi       = \n|area_water_percent     = \n|area_urban_km2         = \n|area_urban_sq_mi       = \n|area_metro_km2         = \n|area_metro_sq_mi       = \n|population_as_of       =\n|population_footnotes   = \n|population_note        = \n|population_total       =  70,629\n|population_density_km2 = \n|population_density_sq_mi = \n|population_metro       =\n|population_density_metro_km2 =\n|population_density_metro_sq_mi =\n|population_urban       = \n|population_density_urban_km2 =\n|population_density_urban_mi2 =\n| timezone = Indochina Time\n| utc_offset = +7\n|latd=|latm=|lats=|latNS=\n|longd=|longm=|longs= |longEW=\n|elevation_footnotes    =  <!--for references: use <ref> </ref> tags-->\n|elevation_m              = \n|elevation_ft           = \n|postal_code_type       =  <!-- enter ZIP code, Postcode, Post code, Postal code... -->\n|postal_code            =\n|area_code              = \n|website                = \n|footnotes              = \n}}\n\n'''S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng District''' is a [[huy\u1ec7n|rural district]] of [[B\u1eafc Giang Province]] in the [[Northeast (Vietnam)|Northeast]] region of Vietnam. It is the easternmost district in the province. As of 2003 it had a population of 70,629.<ref name=\"Statoids\">{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yvn.html|title=Districts of Vietnam|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=March 13, 2009}}</ref> The district covers an area of 844&nbsp;km\u00b2. The district capital lies at [[An Ch\u00e2u (township in B\u1eafc Giang)|An Ch\u00e2u]].<ref name=\"Statoids\"/>   There are some cultural sites here such as: [[Ch\u1ebd pagoda]], [[Female King temple]], [[L\u1ee5c Li\u1ec5u temple]], [[\u0110\u1eb7ng temple]] and [[Ch\u1ebd temple]].\n\n==Administrative divisions==\nThe district is divided administratively into two townships, [[An Ch\u00e2u, B\u1eafc Giang|An Ch\u00e2u]] (district capital) and [[T\u00e2y Y\u00ean T\u1eed]], and the communes of: [[H\u1eefu S\u1ea3n, B\u1eafc Giang|H\u1eefu S\u1ea3n]], [[An L\u1ea1c, B\u1eafc Giang|An L\u1ea1c]], [[V\u00e2n S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|V\u00e2n S\u01a1n]], [[L\u1ec7 Vi\u1ec5n]], [[V\u0129nh An, B\u1eafc Giang|V\u0129nh An]], [[D\u01b0\u01a1ng H\u01b0u]], [[Long S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|Long S\u01a1n]], [[An B\u00e1]], [[Y\u00ean \u0110\u1ecbnh, B\u1eafc Giang|Y\u00ean \u0110\u1ecbnh]], [[Tu\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ea1o]], [[Thanh Lu\u1eadn]], [[C\u1ea9m \u0110\u00e0n]], [[Gi\u00e1o Li\u00eam]], [[\u0110\u1ea1i S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|\u0110\u1ea1i S\u01a1n]] and [[Ph\u00fac S\u01a1n, S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng|Ph\u00fac S\u01a1n]].\n\n121.72&nbsp;km\u00b2 in the southern portion of the district has been designated as the [[T\u00e2y Y\u00ean T\u1eed Nature Reserve]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tay Yen Tu in Viet Nam |publisher=Protected Planet |url=https://www.protectedplanet.net/tay-yen-tu-nature-reserve |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731200044/https://www.protectedplanet.net/tay-yen-tu-nature-reserve |archive-date=31 July 2018 |url-status=live |df=dmy}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|author=Minh Qu\u00fd H\u00e0 |year=2010 |title=Khu b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean T\u00e2y Y\u00ean T\u1eed: gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng sinh h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n |trans-title= T\u00e2y Y\u00ean T\u1eed Nature Reserve: biodiversity conservation value and development potential |language=vi |location=[[Hanoi]] |publisher=Natural Science and Technology Publishing House |oclc=864366107}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Clear}}\n\n{{Districts of Northeast Vietnam}}\n\n{{coord|21.3333|N|106.8500|E|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Son Dong District}}\n[[Category:Districts of B\u1eafc Giang Province]]\n{{BacGiang-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = S\u01a1n \u0110\u1ed9ng Dist